content: Yes, I understand. I will consider the provided information on NSW Residential Building Contract for Small Works between $5000 and $20,000, which is suitable for residential building work where no insurance under the Home Building Compensation Fund is required. It is not to be used for work costing over $20,000 and is ideal for small jobs such as cabinet installation, bathroom renovations, carports, garages, and pergolas that cost less than $20,000.
